		<h1>airport info</h1>
		<p>The closest major airport is LAX, in Los Angeles. Depending on traffic, the drive may be as little as 1 hr. 15 minutes, or as long as 2 hr. 30 minutes. Driving between 10am and 2pm is the best time to drive from LAX to Santa Barbara. The other option would be to fly into Santa Barbara Airport (SBA). However it is fairly limited and tends to be expensive, but still worth considering.</p>


